## Limitations

The findings are based on available data from specific platforms and may not represent the full scope of the issue across different industries or regions. Additionally, some sources may have overlapping information, and the lack of publication dates for certain documents could affect the timeliness of the data. Further research with a broader dataset could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the impact of late shipments on customer inquiries.